---
title: Easy Double American Chicken & Slaw Burger with Fries & Smokey Aioli
description: Those smokey flavours are magical, they have the unbeatable power to make your mouth water. The chicken is stacked up in a burger and smeared with smokey aioli to cast a spell on your tastebuds. The only way to break the spell is to dig in and devour the fries and chicken burger!
